name: The Winnington Occasional Table
description: The Winnington is a handsome occasional table with clean, elegant lines of signature Davidson style and superior design geometry. A rectangular top sits on a square, tapered pedestal base, with an elegant stepped detail, all standing on a facetted base. It is perfect for those looking to complete a smart living room with a cluster of stylish occasional tables or as a single quality piece. Originally designed in high-gloss Macassar ebony, in line with the Art Deco feel of the table, with a beautifully-crafted quartered top, a glossy collar and feet in polished nickel. The Winnington occasional table is available in a wide choice of different coloured timbers in high gloss and satin options; with nickel, brass or antiqued brass detailing to choose from.
